=== Investigative Methods ===
AngelofthyNight's methodology is thorough and sound, at least for a [[stoner]] [[redneck]] [[retard]]. The Paranormal and Ghost Society goes out to cemeteries, historic sites, and other [[boring|totally spooky]] places and takes pictures while Lord Rick leaps around from headstone to headstone acting like a [[douchebag]] with his sword that he carries on investigations. AngelofthyNight then [[photoshop]]s [[semen|orbs]] or other [[shit|masses]] into his pictures to show that it was haunted. According to AngelofthyNight, all of the places he has investigated have been haunted. 

