mankind's wrongdoings?  Or will he watch in the darkness from above and help those that are looking for true salvation such as he was when he came into this world. Today he lives often misunderstood creating miracles that only he could understand as he loves the darkness that mankind has forgotten.  Thus the creature AngelOfThyNight came to be and walks amongst you and life's many paths.|0}}

