Lord Rick also set several of his [[MySpace]] blog entries to private, and, in keeping with his [[internet panhandling]], restricted full access to his [[shit]] website to those who give him [[OL]] or [[IRL]] [[fellatio]], [[attention whore|attention]], or money. Yes, for the low price of $39.99 per year, you too can peruse the entirety of AngelofthyNight's paranoid [[Unwarranted Self Importance|delusions of grandeur]].

